{"comments":"QR Code Data Placement — Zigzag pattern for data modules.\n\n## Data Placement Algorithm\n\nData bits are placed in a zigzag pattern:\n\n1. Start from bottom-right corner\n2. Move upward in 2-column strips\n3. Alternate direction (up/down) for each strip\n4. Skip column 6 (timing pattern)\n5. Skip all function pattern positions\n\n## Module Ordering\n\nWithin each 2-column strip, process right column then left column\nfor each row in the current direction.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Get positions for data modules in zigzag order.\n\nData is placed in a zigzag pattern starting from bottom-right,\nmoving upward in 2-column strips, alternating direction.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","Matrix"],"QRMatrix"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["row",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["col",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[66,71],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Data.purs","start":[66,1]},"title":"getDataModulePositions"},{"children":[],"comments":"Place data bits into the matrix.\n\nTakes array of bits (0 or 1) and places them in zigzag order.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"